}

### Get All Leave Requests
GET http://localhost:8080/api/leave

### Get Specific Leave Request (replace with actual ID from previous responses)
# GET http://localhost:8080/api/leave/your-leave-request-id-here

### Approve Leave Request (replace with actual ID of pending request)
# PUT http://localhost:8080/api/leave/your-leave-request-id-here/approve

### Reject Leave Request (replace with actual ID of pending request)  
# PUT http://localhost:8080/api/leave/your-leave-request-id-here/reject

### Test Invalid JSON (should return 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/leave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeName": "Invalid User",
  "daysRequested": "not-a-number"
}

### Test Missing Fields (should return 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/leave
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeName": "Missing Days"
}

